name: Copilot Task
description: Standard task/issue template for P100-PowerPlatform-ALM
title: "25P###-[Issue Title in Kebab-Case]"
labels: []
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        # Copilot Task Template
        
        **Repository:** Electric-G-Ltd/P100-PowerPlatform-ALM
        
        Use this template to create structured issues that align with P100 governance.

  - type: textarea
    id: objective
    attributes:
      label: Objective
      description: What is the goal of this work?
      placeholder: "e.g., Establish foundational governance documents for P100-PowerPlatform-ALM"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: context
    attributes:
      label: Context
      description: Why is this work needed? What problem does it solve?
      placeholder: "Provide background and business/technical context"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: acceptance_criteria
    attributes:
      label: Acceptance Criteria
      description: How do we know this work is complete? (use checkboxes)
      placeholder: |
        - [ ] Criterion 1
        - [ ] Criterion 2
        - [ ] Criterion 3
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: deliverables
    attributes:
      label: Deliverables
      description: What will be delivered? (files, code, documentation, etc.)
      placeholder: |
        - PR with [description]
        - Documentation updated
        - Tests added
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: textarea
    id: teach_back
    attributes:
      label: Teach-Back (Required)
      description: |
        Explain the professional reasoning behind this work. What will be learned?
        
        Include:
        - **Decision/Work:** What is being done
        - **Professional Reasoning:** Why this approach
        - **What You'll Learn:** Key takeaways
        - **Trade-offs:** Pros and cons considered
      placeholder: |
        ## Teach-Back: [Title]
        
        **Decision:** [What is being done]
        
        **Professional Reasoning:**
        - [Reason 1]
        - [Reason 2]
        
        **What You'll Learn:**
        - [Learning 1]
        - [Learning 2]
        
        **Trade-offs:**
        - Pro: [Benefit]
        - Con: [Cost]
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        ## Naming Convention
        
        Issue titles must follow: **`25P###-Title-In-Kebab-Case`**
        
        - `25` = Year
        - `P` = Project prefix
        - `###` = Sequential number
        - `Title` = Descriptive, kebab-case
        
        Example: `25P001-Project-Governance`